summary: An ordinance approving and confirming the assessment and assessment roll of Local Improvement District No. 1619, for the improvement of 4th Avenue North in the City of Seattle, from McGraw Street to Howell Street, by grading and curbing the same, under Ordinance No. 17201 and levying and assessing the amounts thereof against each parcel of land and part thereof shown in said roll, and providing for the collection thereof.
